7 A veteran who suffers from post-traumatic stress disorder, symptoms of Persian Gulf
8 illness, or injuries connected to tainted, poisoned or adulterated water at Camp Lejeune and such
9 disorder, illness, or injuries have been certified by the Veterans’ Administration as service-
10 connected and who is determined to be 80 per cent disabled by the Veterans’ Administration
